# cos-docs/.dockerignore — keep Docker build context minimal.
# The site/ tree is produced OUTSIDE the Docker build (by the CI workflow)
# and is the ONLY content the image needs. See RESEARCH §4 Pitfall 2.

.git
.gitignore
.github
.planning
.venv*
__pycache__
*.pyc
*.pyo
docs/
mkdocs.yml
scripts/
requirements-docs.txt
.build-all-api-status.md
tests/
README.md
# Explicitly allow (override above with ! lines only if needed; here nothing is needed):
